# unicore-skills repository overview

- This repository stores internal engineering playbooks for Universe Group Head Office (`unicore`).
- Canonical process content lives in `skills/<topic>/SKILL.md`.
- IDE-specific adapters live in:
  - `.claude-plugin/`
  - `.codex-plugin/`
  - `.cursor/rules/`
  - `.windsurf/skills/`
  - `.github/`
- When updating guidance, edit the canonical skill first and then sync the adapter files.
